description: This Chainlink VRF hall of fame Anurak purrs with a rating of 37, and a multiplier of 8x. It has a total score of 296, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, Box for East, Leverage for South, and 8 for West. Anurak has the personality suit of hodler. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/20378-14683-1.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Anurak [296 Votes, Hall of Fame]
